reviewText: This is the rock band, Damn Yankees, not the movie. It features Ted Nugent, Jack Blades, Tommy Shaw and Michael Cartellone. It has videos for "Come Again", "High Enough", "Coming Of Age" and an MTV appearance on "Unplugged", plus behind-the-scenes footage of the band.

this v.c. r. arrived in excelent condition-although a bit pricy for such an old movie, the quality of this reproduction was worth it!
one cannot find this classic in any video store.
